text: Sean Lewis (born April 17, 1992) is an American soccer player who currently plays for FC Tulsa in the USL Championship. ==Career== ===Club=== In January 2015 Lewis signed for Olympia Warriors of the National Premier League in Australia where he led Olympia to a National Premier League top four finish, Victory League Championship, Summer Cup Championship, and a Victory League Cup Championship . In February 2016, Lewis signed for Jacksonville Armada in the NASL.
